---
import Layout from '../../layouts/DRAGONFORGEMEDIA.astro';
---

<Layout title="Home" description="DragonForgeMedia's main page" page="/DragonForgeMedia">
	<div class="p-6">
		<iframe src="https://discord.com/widget?id=1153106771926323270&theme=dark" height="200" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" sandbox="allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts" class=" w-[100%]"></iframe>
		<h5 class="text-center text-2xl">About DragonForgeMedia</h5>
		<p class="text-center">We are a small media studio owned by DragonForgeNEXUS.</p>
		<p class="text-center">As of now, we have no channels, more info in the recommended/recent blog post.</p>
		<div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center pt-3">
			<div class="card w-100% bg-base-100 shadow-xl image-full transition ease-in-out delay-150 hover:scale-105">
				<figure><img src="/imgs/Logos/Banner/Solid/3000x1500/PNG/DRAGONFORGEMEDIA-solid-banner.png" alt="DragonForgeNEXUS banner" /></figure>
				<div class="card-body">
					<h2 class="card-title">Recommended Blog Post</h2>
					<p>Goodbye to the DragonForgeGaming Youtube Channel<br />Say goodbye to the DragonForgeGaming Youtube Channel<br />Media | 2023-11-30</p>
					<div class="card-actions justify-end">
						<a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://blog.dragonforgenexus.xyz/blog/goodbye-dragonforgegaming-youtube-channel/">View</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>